@startuml
title Pet Lifecycle Management Sequence

actor "Catalog Manager" as Manager
participant "Feature Review Workspace" as Workspace
participant "Pet API" as PetAPI
database "Pet Catalog" as Catalog

Manager -> Workspace: Submit new pet details
' operationId: addPet
Workspace -> PetAPI: POST /pet create pet
PetAPI -> Catalog: Persist Pet
PetAPI --> Workspace: Pet created

Manager -> Workspace: Update pet status or metadata
' operationId: updatePet
Workspace -> PetAPI: PUT /pet update pet
PetAPI -> Catalog: Save changed Pet

Manager -> Workspace: Inspect pet by id
' operationId: getPetById
Workspace -> PetAPI: GET /pet/{petId}
PetAPI --> Workspace: Return Pet

Manager -> Workspace: Filter catalog by status
' operationId: findPetsByStatus
Workspace -> PetAPI: GET /pet/findByStatus
PetAPI -> Catalog: Query by Pet.status
PetAPI --> Workspace: Matching pets

Manager -> Workspace: Remove pet from catalog
' operationId: deletePet
Workspace -> PetAPI: DELETE /pet/{petId}
PetAPI -> Catalog: Delete Pet
PetAPI --> Workspace: Pet deleted
@enduml
